1
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,400
Neboj sa, In.

2
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,850
Všetko bude v poriadku.

3
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Neopúšťaj ma.

4
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Prepáč.

5
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Milujem ťa.

6
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Zapamätaj si to.

7
00:01:04,050 --> 00:01:06,000
Neskutočne ťa milujem.

8
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,000
Už nič nehovor!

9
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Prečo mám pocit,
že sa so mnou lúčiš?

10
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,000
Budeme spolu.

11
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Vždy budem s tebou.

12
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,000
Čo to má znamenať?!

13
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,400
Otec.

14
00:02:02,450 --> 00:02:04,500
Nedotýkaj sa môjho syna!

15
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:07,000
Poď sem!

16
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Otec.

17
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,000
Zbláznil si sa?

18
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,000
Milujem ho!

19
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,000
Milujeme sa.

20
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,000
Milujete sa?!

21
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,000
Miluješ ho viac,
ako svojich rodičov?!

22
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Otec.

23
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
Ako mi to chceš vysvetliť?!

24
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,000
Je to moja vina.

25
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,000
Prepáčte.

26
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,000
Prečo sa mi ospravedlňuješ?!

27
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,000
Ja nie som tvoj otec!

28
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
Sme si cudzí!

29
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,500
Otec!

30
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,000
Poď sem!

31
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Neubližuj mu.

32
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,000
Už sa k môjmu synovi nepribližuj!

33
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,000
Korn!

34
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,000
Čo má toto znamenať?
Poď sem!

35
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:50,000
Koľkokrát ti to mám ešte povedať?

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,000
Nechaj toho chlapca na pokoji!

37
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,000
Takže toto je jeho otec?

38
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,000
No a?!

39
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:09,000
Zakázal som môjmu synovi
stretávať sa s mafiánmi, ako ste vy!

40
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,000
Nepozeraj sa na neho!

41
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,000
Otec.

42
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Prepáč.

43
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,000
Nepozeraj sa na neho!

44
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,000
Nemáš s ním nič spoločné!

45
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,500
Prečo si sa zaplietol s niekym,
ako je on?!

46
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,000
Otec, milujeme sa!

47
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,000
Milujem ho.

48
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:12,000
Korn!

49
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,000
Korn, nie!

50
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,000
Nerob to, Korn!

51
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,000
Daj mi tú zbraň.

52
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:36,000
Nerob to, prosím ťa.

53
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,000
Vráť mi tú zbraň.

54
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,000
Pusť ma!

55
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,000
Korn.

56
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,000
In.

57
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,000
Milujem ťa.

58
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,000
Nerob to, prosím ťa.

59
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:09,000
Korn!

60
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:27,000
Neopúšťaj ma!

61
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:32,000
Zostaň so mnou, prosím.

62
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,000
Preber sa, Korn.

63
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,000
Povedz niečo!

64
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,000
Milujem ťa.

65
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:02,000
Povedal si,
že ma nikdy neopustíš!

66
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:05,000
Prečo to takto dopadlo?

67
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,000
Milujeme sa, či nie?

68
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:17,000
Prečo si mi to urobil?

69
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:00,000
Milujem ťa.

70
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:04,000
Nie!
Nerob to!

